{"thag12.1:0.1":"Theragatha 12.1 ","thag12.1:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","thag12.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag12.1:0.4":"Silavattheragatha ","thag12.1:1.1":"“Silamevidha sikkhetha, ","thag12.1:1.2":"asmim loke susikkhitam; ","thag12.1:1.3":"Silanhi sabbasampattim, ","thag12.1:1.4":"upanameti sevitam. ","thag12.1:2.1":"Silam rakkheyya medhavi, ","thag12.1:2.2":"patthayano tayo sukhe; ","thag12.1:2.3":"Pasamsam vittilabhanca, ","thag12.1:2.4":"pecca sagge pamodanam. ","thag12.1:3.1":"Silava hi bahu mitte, ","thag12.1:3.2":"sannamenadhigacchati; ","thag12.1:3.3":"Dussilo pana mittehi, ","thag12.1:3.4":"dhamsate papamacaram. ","thag12.1:4.1":"Avannanca akittinca, ","thag12.1:4.2":"dussilo labhate naro; ","thag12.1:4.3":"Vannam kittim pasamsanca, ","thag12.1:4.4":"sada labhati silava. ","thag12.1:5.1":"Adi silam patittha ca, ","thag12.1:5.2":"kalyanananca matukam; ","thag12.1:5.3":"Pamukham sabbadhammanam, ","thag12.1:5.4":"tasma silam visodhaye. ","thag12.1:6.1":"Vela ca samvaram silam, ","thag12.1:6.2":"cittassa abhihasanam; ","thag12.1:6.3":"Titthanca sabbabuddhanam, ","thag12.1:6.4":"tasma silam visodhaye. ","thag12.1:7.1":"Silam balam appatimam, ","thag12.1:7.2":"silam avudhamuttamam; ","thag12.1:7.3":"Silamabharanam settham, ","thag12.1:7.4":"silam kavacamabbhutam. ","thag12.1:8.1":"Silam setu mahesakkho, ","thag12.1:8.2":"silam gandho anuttaro; ","thag12.1:8.3":"Silam vilepanam settham, ","thag12.1:8.4":"yena vati disodisam. ","thag12.1:9.1":"Silam sambalamevaggam, ","thag12.1:9.2":"silam patheyyamuttamam; ","thag12.1:9.3":"Silam settho ativaho, ","thag12.1:9.4":"yena yati disodisam. ","thag12.1:10.1":"Idheva nindam labhati, ","thag12.1:10.2":"peccapaye ca dummano; ","thag12.1:10.3":"Sabbattha dummano balo, ","thag12.1:10.4":"silesu asamahito. ","thag12.1:11.1":"Idheva kittim labhati, ","thag12.1:11.2":"pecca sagge ca summano; ","thag12.1:11.3":"Sabbattha sumano dhiro, ","thag12.1:11.4":"silesu susamahito. ","thag12.1:12.1":"Silameva idha aggam, ","thag12.1:12.2":"pannava pana uttamo; ","thag12.1:12.3":"Manussesu ca devesu, ","thag12.1:12.4":"silapannanato jayan”ti. ","thag12.1:12.5":"… Silavo thero …. "}